long_desc.thetext: Plan Mylyn 3.12 release: http://projects.eclipse.org/projects/mylyn/releases/3.12

Products in this release:
* Mylyn Commons: 3.12 * Mylyn Context: 3.12 * Mylyn Tasks: 3.12 * Mylyn Incubator: 3.12 * Mylyn Builds: 1.4 * Mylyn Docs: 2.1 * Mylyn Reviews: 2.3 * Mylyn Versions: 1.4
I have set the release date to Wednesday, June 25, 2014 which coincides with Luna.
I merged the following change onto e_4_4_m_3_12_x: * https://git.eclipse.org/r/#/c/26324/

I back ported the following changes for 3.12:
c6d1aba4e0ae2bc2c9d42d3c682434db7cbb840c (fix annotations in ARC) ccf683f95e4397fb7ac0303fe47e7bc2dd10e620 (remove extraneous check)

Hi Folks,
Couple of quick items for the Luna release:
- * Submit your IP Logs ASAP.
- Could you please add some additional information to the release review documentation in the description section. Namely, what does the release implement or fix; what would users find interesting about the release.
- Please seek PMC approval for the review materials.
Cheers,
Richard
